  <brief_title>Changes in Incretins Response and Glycemic Control After Gastric Bypass Surgery in Type 2 Diabetic Patients Versus Healthy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Incretins Response and Glycemic Control: Pre Diet, After Conventional Weight Loss and in the Early Postoperative Phase After Gastric Bypass in T2D-patients.</official_title>
